OL,3,CGreat Western Railway train services
OL,4,Cto be nationalised
OL,6,FGreat Western Railway train services
OL,7,Fwill be nationalised later this year,
OL,8,Fthe Department for Transport has
OL,9,Fannounced.
OL,11,FThe rail service will be taken into
OL,12,Fpublic ownership on 13 December 2026,
OL,13,Fmaking it the 11th operator with a UK
OL,14,FGovernment contract to make the switch.
OL,16,FGWR is one of Wales' main operators
OL,17,Falongside Transport for Wales. It
OL,18,Flinks south Wales with London.
