OL,3,CGreat Western Railway train services
OL,4,Cto be nationalised
OL,6,FTransport for Wales has been
OL,7,Fnationalised since 2021 after the
OL,8,FWelsh Government took over running of
OL,9,FWales and border rail services.
OL,11,FGWR said it welcomed the "clarity"
OL,12,Fprovided in the announcement.
OL,14,FA Department for Transport
OL,15,Fspokesperson said: "This is another
OL,16,Fsignificant moment for the
OL,17,FGovernment's flagship public ownership
OL,18,Fprogramme and brings a simpler, more
OL,19,Freliable network under Great British
OL,20,FRailways a step closer.
OL,26,@wD@TOU
