PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F465A1778351315
OL,3,CGreat Western Railway train services
OL,4,Cto be nationalised
OL,6,F"The Government is delivering on its
OL,7,Fcommitment to bring services back into
OL,8,Fpublic ownership and put passengers,
OL,9,Fnot shareholders, at the heart of our
OL,10,Frailways."
OL,12,FA Great Western Railway spokesperson
OL,13,Fsaid: "We welcome the clarity provided
OL,14,Fby (today's) announcement and will
OL,15,Fcontinue to work closely with the
OL,16,FDepartment for Transport as we move
OL,17,Finto public ownership.
