OL,3,CGreat Western Railway train services
OL,4,Cto be nationalised
OL,6,F"Throughout this process, our priority
OL,7,Fwill be maintaining a punctual,
OL,8,Freliable service for customers while
OL,9,Fcontinuing to support regional growth
OL,10,Fand connectivity across our network."
